1l-1-1%206-1c6-1%2013-4%2012-5l-5%202c-13%203-37%200-43-7l-3-2c-1%200-1%201%201%203'%20fill='%23557a95'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.3157894736842106,"src":"/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/ea4ab/me.jpg","srcSet":"/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/477ba/me.jpg 175w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/06776/me.jpg 350w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/ea4ab/me.jpg 700w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/3055e/me.jpg 1050w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/eff08/me.jpg 1400w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/0fc52/me.jpg 1420w","srcWebp":"/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/89afa/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/9fca7/me.webp 175w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/37a4e/me.webp 350w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/89afa/me.webp 700w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/78e7a/me.webp 1050w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/03d34/me.webp 1400w,\n/static/0f41ea1849b956c1c08522ee509c5109/004e3/me.webp 1420w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"skills":["DriveWays","MEXCOWalk","RNA-binding Proteins","Predicting Clinical Outcomes in Neuroblastoma."]},"html":"<p>Hello! I am a computational biologist based in Antalya, TR. Currently I'm doing my Masters in computational group at <a href=\"https://antalya.edu.tr/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Antalya Bilim University</a>. I am specialized in applying machine learning techniques to challenging problems in Biology especially Cancer.</p>\n<p>I graduate in 2017 from Antalya Bilim University, majoring in Electronics Engineering as well as Computer Engineering.\nI am moving soon to NYC to join <a href=\"https://compbio.triiprograms.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Tri-I PhD program in Computational Biology and Medicine</a>\nHere are a few projects I've been working on recently:</p>\n<!-- (https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.04.01.015388v1.full) -->\n<!-- (https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/547653v2) -->"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Visiting Research","company":"Vector Research Institute","location":"Toronto, CA","range":"Jun - Sep 2019","url":"https://vectorinstitute.ai/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Visiting the lab of <a href=\"http://www.morrislab.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Prof. Quaid Morris</a>  at the Vector Institute working on using predictive models to predict RNA-Binding Proteins binding site target</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Research Assistant","company":"Computational Biology Group","location":"Antalya, TR","range":"Oct 2018- today","url":"http://www.hkazanlab.com/index.html"},"html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.04.01.015388v1.full\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">DriveWays</a>: a novel algorithm to identify overlapping cancer driver modules applied to TCGA multi-omics data.</li>\n<li>Performed the classification and survival analysis for a novel approach named <a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/547653v2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">MEXCOWalk</a>for identifying cancer driver modules.</li>\n<li>Co-supervised a final year undergraduate student’s independent study project.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Senior Project","company":"Machine Learning Lab","location":"Antalya, TR","range":"Feb - Sep 2017 ","url":"http://www.hkazanlab.com/index.html"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Participated in The Neuroblastoma Data Integration Challenge hosted by CAMDA to improve the prediction of clinical outcome, survival time, or disease mechanisms vs the original expression-only study by the FDA SEQC.</li>\n<li>The results of the project were accepted for an oral presentation in the 16th annual international conference on Intelligent Systems for Molecular Biology (ISMB) with invitation to submit the full length paper for fast track to the CAMDA Proceedings special issue of Biology Direct</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Intern","company":"Digital Media and Data Reconstruction","location":"Shanghai Jiao Tong Univ, China","range":"Jun - Sep 2016","url":""},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Interned in the lab of Professor Lizhuang Ma.</li>\n<li>Learned the principles of machine and deep learning methods with special focus on convolutional neural networks.</li>\n<li>Built a face recognition system based on GoogleNet neural network, achieving an accuracy of 94% on LFW dataset.</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Spotify Profile","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='250'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20250'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%2037a269%20269%200%20002%2048L1%2096l-1%2077v77h401V0H0v37m10-24c-3%203-3%207%200%2010%207%206%2016-1%2013-9-3-5-9-6-13-1m205%2020c0%202-2%203-10%203-3%200-3%201-3%203%200%203%200%203-3%203s-3%200-3%202c1%201%200%202-1%203-2%201-1%202%203%202%203%200%204%200%204%202s0%202-4%202h-5l2%201c2%200%202%201%202%202l-2%201-2%201%204%201c4%200%205%201%206%203l-5%201c-2%200-4%200-3%201l1%203%202%202%201%202%201%201%201-2-2-2c-2%200-1-3%201-4%201%200%202%200%202%202l1%202c1%200%202%201%202%203%200%205%201%206%205%206%202%200%202%200%202-3-1-5-2-7-3-6-2%200-3-4-2-6%201-1%201-1-1-1h-2c3-2%202-3-2-3-3%200-4%200-4-2%200-3%2010-3%2011%200l2%204%202%202c0%202%205%202%208%201h3v1c0%202%202%203%202%200%201-2%200-5-1-5-2%200-3-5-2-8%202-3%201-3-2-2-1%201-2%201-2-1-1-2-4-1-5%201%200%203-2%203-3%200-1-2%200-3%203-3s3%200%202-3-3-4-6-1h-2l-2-1c-2%201-4-2-3-3%202-1%2019-3%2019-1l1%201%201-1%201-2c1-1%200-1-4-1-4%201-5%201-5-1l-1-1v1m13%20181c0%207%201%207%204%204%201-2%202-3%201-4v-1c3-1%204%201%204%204%200%202%201%203%202%203%202%200%202-1%202-6v-7h-13v7m-1%2023v7h6l7%201h-7c-9%200-8%202%202%202%206%200%209-